ZH: 我们需要您亲自来公司签字。
EN: We need you to come to the company in person to sign the documents.
ZH: 请在这里签字确认你的身份。
EN: Please sign here to confirm your identity.
ZH: 这是一个重要文件，请您签字。
EN: This is an important document, please sign.
ZH: 签字后，请将文件放在桌子上。
EN: After signing, please place the document on the table.
ZH: 你必须亲自到银行签字才能办理手续。
EN: You must go to the bank in person to sign before processing the paperwork.
ZH: 请签字并填写你的联系信息。
EN: Please sign and provide your contact information.
ZH: 老板已经签字批准这项计划了。
EN: The boss has signed to approve this plan.
ZH: 让我们签字协议，开始我们的合作吧。
EN: Let's sign the agreement and start our collaboration.
ZH: 请在这里签字确认你的参加意愿。
EN: Please sign here to confirm your willingness to participate.
ZH: 他用红色笔在文件上签字了。
EN: He signed the document with a red pen.
ZH: 签字后，请将文件交给我。
EN: After signing, please hand the document over to me.
ZH: 请在这里签字并输入你的密码。
EN: Please sign here and enter your password.
ZH: 他们需要你马上过去签字。
EN: They need you to come over and sign immediately.
ZH: 请注意，在文件上签字之前不要忘记阅读。
EN: Please remember to read before signing on the document.
ZH: 你可以用蓝色或黑色笔在这里签字。
EN: You can use a blue or black pen to sign here.
ZH: 在签字的同时，请仔细阅读文件内容。
EN: While signing, please read the content of the document carefully.
ZH: 他已经签字同意加入我们的团队。
EN: He has signed to agree to join our team.
ZH: 请在文件右下角签字并注明日期。
EN: Please sign at the bottom right of the document and date it.
ZH: 为了确认您的身份，请在这里签字。
EN: To confirm your identity, please sign here.
ZH: 让我看看你签字的笔迹是否和之前一样。
EN: Let me see if the handwriting of your signature matches the previous one.
